      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You must extract the requested information from the provided paper text and output it as a single valid JSON object. The output must be understandable without knowlegde of the provided paper text.\n\nFollow these rules:\n1. Output ONLY valid JSON.\n2. Do NOT include any text outside the JSON object.\n3. Do NOT invent information. Use only what is explicitly in the paper text.\n4. If information is missing, use the string: \"Not specified in the available information\".\n5. Lists must be JSON arrays.\n6. Field names must match the request exactly.\n7. NEVER add new fields to the output template.\n8. Include only information that is explicitly requested.\n9. Refer to the input text of the paper as \"the paper\" or similar.\n\n\nREQUEST:\n{{ $json.Prompt }}\n\nPAPER TEXT:\n{{ $('Extract from PDFs').item.json.text }}\n\nYour response must follow this format exactly:\n\n{{ $json.Output_format }}\n\n",
